    "description": "A program that prepares individuals to assist a teacher in regular classroom settings or in providing instruction and supervision to special student populations, such as bilingual/bicultural students, special education students, adult learners, and students learning English.  Includes instruction in techniques of general classroom supervision, maintaining order, assisting with lessons and carrying out related assignments.",
