    "title": "Game Design and Interactive Media",
    "description": "A program that focuses on the design, development, and programming of interactive media entertainment, including computer and video games, virtual environments,  Internet applications, and other interactive media. Includes instruction in theory of games, turn-based games, real-time games, visual and interactive design, story development, animation, simulation, and programming.",
