    "description": "A program that prepares individuals creatively and technically to express emotions, ideas, or inner visions through representation by lines made on a surface.  Includes instruction in eye-hand coordination; line, value, shape, and perspective; figure and still life drawing; the use of media such as pen and ink, pencil, charcoal, pastel, and brush; and personal style development.",
