    "title": "Hospitality and Tourism FAQ",
    "description": "<p>As a worker in Hospitality and Tourism, you help people have fun by providing food, lodging, guidance, or other recreational services. You may work behind a counter, in a kitchen, on a sports field, or more.</p>\r\n",
