    "id": "b7754267-38d7-4093-8d3e-230c03f358b7",
    "title": "10 Fastest Growing Jobs in Finance ",
    "description": "<h2>What are the fastest growing careers in Finance?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Finance careers include jobs in planning, services for financial and investment planning, banking, insurance, and business financial management.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Here is a list of 10 fastest growing careers in the Finance career cluster with substantial job demand.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n\t<li><a href=\"https://bigfuture.collegeboard.org/careers/financial-manager\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"[Opens in a New Window]\">Financial Managers</a>: Projected Job Growth: 9.10%<br />\r\n\tPlan, direct, or coordinate accounting, investing, banking, insurance, securities, and other financial activities of a branch, office, or department of an establishment.</li>\r\n\t<li><a href=\"https://bigfuture.collegeboard.org/careers/treasurer-and-controller\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"[Opens in a New Window]\">Treasurers and Controllers</a>: Projected Job Growth: 9.10%<br />\r\n\tDirect financial activities, such as planning, procurement, and investments for all or part of an organization.</li>\r\n\t<li><a href=\"https://bigfuture.collegeboard.org/careers/insurance-sales-agent\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"[Opens in a New Window]\">Insurance Sales Agents</a>: Projected Job Growth: 8.52%<br />\r\n\tSell life, property, casualty, health, automotive, or other types of insurance. May refer clients to independent brokers, work as an independent broker, or be employed by an insurance company.</li>\r\n\t<li><a href=\"https://bigfuture.collegeboard.org/careers/personal-financial-advisor\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"[Opens in a New Window]\">Personal Financial Advisors</a>: Projected Job Growth: 7.75%<br />\r\n\tAdvise clients on financial plans using knowledge of tax and investment strategies, securities, insurance, pension plans, and real estate. Duties include assessing clients' assets, liabilities, cash flow, insurance coverage, tax status, and financial objectives. May also buy and sell financial assets for clients.</li>\r\n\t<li><a href=\"https://bigfuture.collegeboard.org/careers/tax-preparer\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"[Opens in a New Window]\">Tax Preparers</a>: Projected Job Growth: 5.98%<br />\r\n\tPrepare tax returns for individuals or small businesses.</li>\r\n\t<li><a href=\"https://bigfuture.collegeboard.org/careers/financial-analyst\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"[Opens in a New Window]\">Financial and Investment Analysts</a>: Projected Job Growth: 5.30%<br />\r\n\tConduct quantitative analyses of information involving investment programs or financial data of public or private institutions, including valuation of businesses.</li>\r\n\t<li><a href=\"https://bigfuture.collegeboard.org/careers/accountant-or-auditor\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://bigfuture.collegeboard.org/careers/accountant-or-auditor\">Accountants and Auditors</a>: Projected Job Growth: 4.84%<br />\r\n\tExamine, analyze, and interpret accounting records to prepare financial statements, give advice, or audit and evaluate statements prepared by others. Install or advise on systems of recording costs or other financial and budgetary data.&nbsp;</li>\r\n\t<li><a href=\"https://bigfuture.collegeboard.org/careers/financial-quantitative-analyst\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://bigfuture.collegeboard.org/careers/accountant-or-auditor\">Financial Quantitative Analysts</a>: Projected Job Growth: 4.64%<br />\r\n\tDevelop quantitative techniques to inform securities investing, equities investing, pricing, or valuation of financial instruments. Develop mathematical or statistical models for risk management, asset optimization, pricing, or relative value analysis.</li>\r\n\t<li><a href=\"https://bigfuture.collegeboard.org/careers/fraud-examiner-investigator-or-analyst\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"[Opens in a New Window]\">Fraud Examiners, Investigators and Analysts</a>: Projected Job Growth: 4.64%<br />\r\n\tObtain evidence, take statements, produce reports, and testify to findings regarding resolution of fraud allegations. May coordinate fraud detection and prevention activities.</li>\r\n\t<li><a href=\"https://bigfuture.collegeboard.org/careers/securities-commodities-and-financial-services-sales-agent\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"[Opens in a New Window]\">Financial Sales Agents</a>: Projected Job Growth: 3.17%<br />\r\n\tBuy and sell securities or commodities in investment and trading firms, or provide financial services to businesses and individuals. May advise customers about stocks, bonds, mutual funds, commodities, and market conditions.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>This list was developed to provide meaningful information, so only occupations with a minimum number of available jobs were included.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Explore more <a href=\"https://bigfuture.collegeboard.org/career-search/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"[Opens in a New Window]\">careers </a>on BigFuture. Not sure where to start? Get a list of careers that match your interests with our easy 15-minute <a href=\"https://bigfuture.collegeboard.org/career-search/career-quiz\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"[Opens in a New Window]\">Career Quiz</a>.&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n",
    "readTime": "5 min read",
    "audience": "Student",
    "category": "College Planning",
    "requiresLogin": true,
    "language": "English"
