    "id": "a25d244c-9878-4df4-9e89-6e920b84be27",
    "title": "Information Technology Career Path Resources",
    "description": "<p>In an increasingly digital world, Information Technology (IT) plays a critical role today and the IT industry is one of the largest contributors to the economy.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Information Technology relates to the design, development and support of software, hardware, multimedia and systems integration services. Employment in computer and information technology occupations is one of the fastest growing fields – from 2020 to 2030 it is projected to grow 13 percent.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n",
