    "id": "b53028a7-4ebb-4376-a569-60399b2b9828",
    "title": "College Costs: FAQ",
    "description": "<p>College may seem expensive. In reality, though, it’s often more affordable than you think. The costs depend on what college you go to and how much financial aid you receive.</p>\r\n",
    "readTime": "5 min read",
    "audience": "Student",
